Silicon carbide power semiconductors market is segmented by device, wafer size, and application. By device, the market is categorized into MOSFET, Schottky Barrier Diode (SBD), and others. The MOSFET segment is expected to dominate the market owing to its high demand in various applications due to its high efficiency and power handling capabilities. The Schottky Barrier Diode (SBD) segment is also anticipated to witness significant growth due to its low forward voltage drop and fast switching speed. In terms of wafer size, the market is divided into 2-inch, 4-inch, and 6-inch and above. The 6-inch and above segment is projected to show substantial growth as it allows for the production of more efficient power devices. Based on application, the market is segmented into industrial, automotive, telecommunication, consumer electronics, and others.

